sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Browser
    participant Main as main.rs
    participant Listener as TcpListener
    participant Stream as TcpStream
    participant Buffer as buffer [0; 1024]
    participant Response as response String

    Note over Main,Listener: 启动阶段
    Main->>Listener: bind("127.0.0.1:8080")
    Listener-->>Main: listener 就绪

    loop for stream in listener.incoming()
        Browser->>Main: GET / HTTP/1.1
        Main->>Listener: incoming()
        Listener-->>Main: stream.unwrap()
        Main->>Buffer: let mut buffer = [0; 1024]
        Main->>Stream: read(&mut buffer)
        Stream->>Buffer: 请求报文写入 buffer
        Buffer-->>Main: println!(&buffer[..])
        Main->>Response: format!(headers + body)
        Response-->>Main: response String
        Main->>Stream: write_all(response.as_bytes())
        Stream->>Browser: HTTP/1.1 200 OK\nWelcome to Rust VPN Phase 1!
        Note over Browser: 浏览器展示文本
    end

    Note over Main,Response: 当前代码未解析 HTTP 请求，只是读取原始字节并返回固定响应
